subject: Football
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Quarterback Garrett Gilbert ran for two touchdowns and Texas’ defense shut down Taylor Martinez to lead the visiting Longhorns to a 20-13 upset of fifth-ranked Nebraska on Saturday.
